  [ Stefan Sauer ]
  * Use a high prio idle handler for keyboard inputs.
  * window: defer the shown() signal until the window is on the screen

  [ David Lechner ]
  * Motors: update for kernel release cycle 10 changes
  * Bump GIR/package version
  * Use udev properties for driver_name and address
  * Ui: Make dialog size proportional to window size
  * Fix critical message on InputDialog
  * Draw dialogs in front of status bar
  * Fix label preferred width/height in cases where there is negative margin

